trans-unit.source: Represents a read-only collection of <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.ManifestSignatureInformation"></xref> objects.
trans-unit.target: Representa uma coleção só de leitura de <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.ManifestSignatureInformation"> </xref> objetos.

trans-unit.source: To get a ManifestSignatureInformationCollection collection, call one of the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.ManifestSignatureInformation.VerifySignature%2A> method overloads.
trans-unit.target: Para obter uma coleção de ManifestSignatureInformationCollection, chamar um do <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.ManifestSignatureInformation.VerifySignature%2A>sobrecargas do método.</xref:System.Security.Cryptography.ManifestSignatureInformation.VerifySignature%2A>

trans-unit.source: Each collection contains a <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.ManifestSignatureInformation> object for each manifest that was verified by the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.ManifestSignatureInformation.VerifySignature%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Cada coleção contém um <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.ManifestSignatureInformation>objeto para cada manifesto que foi verificado pelo <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.ManifestSignatureInformation.VerifySignature%2A>método.</xref:System.Security.Cryptography.ManifestSignatureInformation.VerifySignature%2A> </xref:System.Security.Cryptography.ManifestSignatureInformation>
